-CSS and other beautification
-general drying up of the code, adding config files, etc.
-support for mp3 streams
-support for browsers other than chrome (firefox works if you use icecast instead of the builtin streamer. Maybe mpd isn't sending the MIME type?)
-graceful fallback to jorbis or other player for older browsers


